<headline>Severe Weather Statement issued July 03 at 6:02PM EDT until July 03 at 10:00PM EDT by NWS Blacksburg</headline>
<description>...THE SEVERE THUNDERSTORM WARNING FOR
SOUTHEASTERN CHARLOTTE AND EAST CENTRAL HALIFAX COUNTIES IS
CANCELLED...
The storm which prompted the warning has weakened below severe
limits, and has exited the warned area. Therefore, the warning has
been cancelled.
A Severe Thunderstorm Watch remains in effect until 1000 PM EDT for
north central North Carolina...and central and south central
Virginia.</description>
